Author: jjyochi
Text: here’s a tip tho, if you tend to binge in a certain place (mine was my bed) try to stay away from that area for a bit or if the urge hits you to binge go somewhere else, drink a coffee, etc. i always binged in my bed bc i associated my bed with binging. once i started going there only to sleep the binging mostly stopped. (this might not help you but it helped me)
